-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/01_09_Succession_S04-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/succession">继任</a></em>演员莎拉·斯努克谈到了该剧大结局中被删减的一个场景。下面有剧透。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>电视剧《睁开眼睛》第四季第 10 集中，当罗伊兄弟姐妹——肯德尔（杰里米·斯特朗饰）、罗曼（基兰·卡尔金饰）和希夫（斯努克饰）——参加董事会时，节目达到了戏剧性的高潮。投票将决定 Waystar Royco 的领导地位和未来。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-recaps/succession-recap-season-four-episode-one-the-munsters-3419083"><em>《继承》</em>第四季第一集回顾：交易、戏剧和离婚</a></strong></li></ul><p>就在希夫即将投票选举她的兄弟肯德尔作为新任首席执行官和已故父亲（布莱恩·考克斯饰）的继任者时，她临阵退缩并在会议中途退出了房间。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="希夫背叛肯德尔 - 继承结局" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/es17PtDeHRU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>随后，她与兄弟姐妹发生了一场激烈的争吵，期间她告诉她的兄弟：“我爱你，但我他妈的受不了你。” She also tells Kendall that she can&#39;t vote for him because he&#39;s killed someone, referring to the moment in the season one finale when he gets into a car accident with a waiter from Shiv&#39;s wedding.</p><p> Shiv leaves the confrontation and votes against her brother, which means that Lukas Matsson&#39;s (Alexander Skarsgård) GoJo deal goes ahead and Shiv&#39;s husband Tom Wambsgans (Matthew Macfadyen) becomes the new CEO.</p><p> In a new interview with <em><a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/succession-sarah-snook-tom-wambsgans-ceo-finale-1235684841/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Variety</a></em> , Snook revealed one extra scene was filmed twice that depicted her character returning to the conference room to cast her vote, rather than it lingering on the two brothers after the argument becomes physical.</p><p> She explained: “The way that [director] Mark Mylod runs the scenes, he will let it run. I left the aquarium of the boys fighting on the floor, and it was so much fun to just saunter, basically, over to the boardroom, stick my head in and go, &#39;No,&#39; and then walk off. It wasn&#39;t like a big scene or anything like that. </p><figure id="attachment_3387560" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3387560" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3387560" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new.jpg" alt="Succession season 4" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Succession-season-4-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3387560" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Succession&#39; season four CREDIT: HBO</figcaption></figure><p> “It was really depressingly easy for Shiv at that moment to just go, &#39;Yeah.绝对不。 No. And I feel confident with that decision.&#39; And then the fallout after that of realising that Tom is CEO, and where do I stand and all of that — I guess that processing comes as it&#39;s been signed in the other boardroom scene with Matsson, and in the car.”</p><p> Snook added: “And then after, once the camera&#39;s finished rolling, where does she go now?”</p><p> The actor also explained that the fight scene between Kendall and Roman was originally meant to be more between Shiv and Kendall.</p><p> “But what ended up happening, which was far more honest and realistic to the scene, is that when Shiv goes to leave, Jeremy grabs my hand.”</p><p> Snook, who was pregnant at the time, said the scene “ended up being fine in terms of my safety, and much better in terms of the scene”.</p><p> In other <em>Succession</em> news, Brian Cox recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/brian-cox-thinks-succession-season-four-twist-happened-too-early-3448120">suggested that the show&#39;s major season four twist happened “too early”</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sarah-snook-reveals-succession-scene-that-was-cut-from-the-finale-3477221">Sarah Snook reveals &#39;Succession&#39; scene that was cut from the finale</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
